{"tid":980323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爸爸冇錢買switch比我，叫我參加填色比賽拎","createTime":"2019-01-13T12:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T15:55:53.000Z","uid":53351,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"707da8ccea7e09a0fa5ddecd48895d9acc425079","tid":980323,"uid":53351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"三個月前表哥飲茶拎咗部switch出黎同我玩，我好想要。<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企求爸爸買比我。<br />\n<br />\n第二日，爸爸拎左盒顏色筆同我講：「爸爸冇錢買比你，但你可以靠自己，得到你想要既野。」<br />\n<br />\n跟住果幾日，我拎住填色比賽既畫，好小心咁唔油出界，跟住卡通入邊咁油，真係好辛苦。<br />\n我以為我已經畫得好靚。<br />\n<br />\n但係，我都係拎唔到switch<br />\n佢地真係畫得好靚<br />\n爸爸叫我下次努力，人地得我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47a0c63f63f0322cb15b64ae923469c9b6ece27","tid":980323,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"返屋企打飛機啦"},{"pid":"3ff6a76c314f410ad9236b2d3be4e0147bbe4b44","tid":980323,"uid":164980,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"964ee129395c417bb7d722979524193c6ee16cd7","tid":980323,"uid":218977,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e3f1249363541c549f79dc6cb842bb532faec1c","tid":980323,"uid":229883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔叫王叔叔買俾你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ca18165c48455482adaf175ce83a211095feab","tid":980323,"uid":19638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"小妹哭了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f122aba00f7e3c0169559cf460f2d4822278a4b","tid":980323,"uid":183417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f4a40bf2342b1d5d3b2c643f85097a2210b2a7cc","tid":980323,"uid":82482,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"repl